Cloverfaust is the forum app designed and developed by Evan Walsh

It is powered by CodeIgniter: http://codeigniter.com/

Server requirements:
	
	- PHP 4/5
	- MySQL
	- Magic :]

To install Cloverfaust, follow these instructions:

	- Upload all the files contained in this release, including
	  .htaccess, core/, index.php, license.txt, user_guide/, and views/
	
	- Navigate to the place where Cloverfaust was uploaded with your
	  web browser.  Example: http://example.com/cloverfaust/
	
	- Cloverfaust will automatically load the installer and you must now
	  enter all your site's details to continue
	
	- You're done!